                "invention-title": [
                    "Water body phosphate oxygen isotope pretreatment sample preparation method for in-situ enrichment material preparation",
                    "一种原位富集材料制备水体磷酸盐氧同位素前处理制样方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a pretreatment sample preparation method for preparing a water phosphate oxygen isotope from an in-situ enrichment material. The method comprises the following steps: preparing a zirconium-loaded resin material; performing in-situ enrichment in a water body; taking out after a proper period of time and eluting phosphate; adding phosphorus-free activated carbon and then adjusting the pH value of the filtrate to 5.8; adding a cerous nitrate solution to adjust the pH until cerous phosphate precipitate is generated; washing the precipitate, adding nitric acid for dissolving, adding cation exchange resin, and oscillating overnight; transferring the filtrate to a centrifugal tube, adjusting the pH value to 8, and adding a silver nitrate solution to generate silver phosphate precipitate; and adding a 15% hydrogen peroxide solution, washing, freezing and drying. The method can effectively avoid collection of a large number of water body samples, the zirconium-loaded resin is easily available in raw material, simple in preparation process and low in cost, is hardly influenced by common anions in the water body in the adsorption process of phosphate, and can meet the preparation requirement only by four days in the actual application water body, so that the process is simplified, and the cost is reduced. And time and economic cost are saved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种原位富集材料制备水体磷酸盐氧同位素前处理制样方法，其包括以下步骤：制备锆负载树脂材料；放置水体中原位富集；适当时间后取出洗脱磷酸盐；加入无磷活性炭后调节滤液ph值至5.8；加入硝酸铈溶液调节ph至生成磷酸铈沉淀；沉淀洗净后加入硝酸溶解，加入阳离子交换树脂振荡过夜；滤液转移至离心管后调节ph值至8，加入硝酸银溶液生成磷酸银沉淀；加入15％过氧化氢溶液后洗净冷冻干燥。本发明方法能有效避免采集大量水体样品，且锆负载树脂原料易得、制备流程简单、成本低廉，在对磷酸盐的吸附过程中几乎不受水体常见阴离子影响，在实际应用水体中富集时间仅需四天可达到制备要求，从而简化流程，节约时间和经济成本。"
                }
